data_sources.description: Contains data on forest surfaces in Romania from 1990 to 2019, categorized by region and type (Hardwood, Softwood, Other).
GeoJSON file containing geographic data (coordinates) for Romanian counties.
Another GeoJSON file with data for Romanian regions and their population.

data_variables.name: data_df
data_variables.description: DataFrame containing the forest surfaces data, including total, Hardwood, Softwood, and Other categories across different regions and years.

data_variables.name: data_county_df
data_variables.description: Filtered DataFrame from data_df containing only data for specific counties in Romania.

data_variables.name: county_lat_long_df
data_variables.description: DataFrame that holds latitude and longitude for each county, derived from the geoJSON file.

data_variables.name: county_population_df
data_variables.description: DataFrame containing the population data for counties, sourced from the geoJSON file.

flows_to: charts and maps visualizing forest surface data by category and year.
